name: Bone RUsh
summary: Hits 2-5 times in a turn. There is a 1/3 chance it will hit 2 or 3 times, and 1/6 4 or 5 times.
viability: On average, you'll hit this around 3-4 times, giving it an average of about 80 base power. It isn't a very good move, as a result. Not when Earthquake or Bonemerang exist.
